{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "7f7f9a8e-2f1e-4c99-9c9d-6f0c0d2fd7b1",
    "name": "CanonBridge Local Demo - REST API and Kafka Flows",
    "description": "Customer-facing local demo collection for CanonBridge.\n\nDemo opens with Mapping Studio login, not health checks. The main story is:\n1. Login to Studio.\n2. Show one REST external system and its auth detail.\n3. Show raw REST response before CanonBridge changes it.\n4. Show request mapping and response mapping metadata.\n5. Run CanonBridge proxy before a Studio mapping edit.\n6. Edit the response mapping in Studio, then rerun the same proxy request to show the response shape changed.\n7. Move to Kafka: raw partner event on partner.raw.events becomes canonical event on canonical.events.\n\nUse Appendix - Pre-demo Checks only before the meeting or for troubleshooting.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
